{"tid":1522983,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家唔好諗點捉鬼，係要諗點救人","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T15:33:31.000Z","uid":169801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f61ee0476e942e9913f172d4c8ebc9c3710e0f5f","tid":1522983,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平時唔洗捉鬼，平時唔洗捉鬼，平時唔洗捉鬼</span></span>，有鬼就當佢幫我(幫我哋掉汽油擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有等佢現影出手㩒低我地手足既時候，圍過去</span></span>，一方面可以防止佢逃走，一方面可以係最後既保護線防止打錯人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果佢係狗會即刻反擊</span></span>，如果佢係手足，會解釋，如果佢係狗，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家識點做</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBTW，呢招只可以用來對付鬼離防線好遠就捉人，如果鬼同速龍合作起衝鋒時先捉人，暫時未諗到解法，不過暫時睇太混亂，鬼捉人既效率都會下降"},{"pid":"b235d0822f804afa4d0fc168b1caf6388fcffe81","tid":1522983,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:08:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7badf128bd7158763d6bdeedd9a531f880dc3e42","tid":1522983,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c76d61513e3e7799104c497103dc35c310c2fe8","tid":1522983,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:17:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"833f06a89c853fded5cb525dac11c3c70cc5cb87","tid":1522983,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b9c6fef5487642c990e1f652dfe7c4c38abb3f4","tid":1522983,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19793847b5fa366f614b72cb41da32af515714a3","tid":1522983,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"唔捉鬼但係要防鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces